OL,3,CRhondda Tunnel reopening plans get
OL,4,Cmajor boost as planning application
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FAmbitious plans to turn a disused
OL,8,FVictorian railway tunnel into Europe's
OL,9,Flongest cycling tunnel have taken a
OL,10,Fstep forward.
OL,12,FRhondda Cynon Taf Council's planning
OL,13,Fcommittee has granted permission for
OL,14,Fcampaigners to excavate the buried
OL,15,FBlaencwm entrance of the Rhondda
OL,16,FTunnel.
OL,18,FThe tunnel, which links the Rhondda
OL,19,FFawr and Afan Valleys, opened in 1890,
OL,20,Fbut closed to trains in 1970. It was
OL,21,Fsealed completely in 1980.
