OL,3,CRhondda Tunnel reopening plans get
OL,4,Cmajor boost as planning application
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FSince 2014, the Rhondda Tunnel Society
OL,8,Fhas campaigned to reopen it, proposing
OL,9,Fto turn it into a global destination
OL,10,Ffor cycling and walking.
OL,12,FBoth entrances to the tunnel have been
OL,13,Fcovered over and landscaped, with
OL,14,Faccess only possible through a
OL,15,Fventilation shaft on the Blaengwynfi
OL,16,Fside or a narrow access pipe at the
OL,17,FRhondda end.
OL,19,FCampaigners hope reopening one
OL,20,Fentrance will allow easier access for
OL,21,Finspection and maintenance work.
