OL,7,FExcavating the second portal is
OL,8,Fconsidered more complex due to its
OL,9,Fdepth, but campaigners are confident
OL,10,Fthe work could be carried out once
OL,11,Ffunding is secured.
OL,13,FStephen Mackey, the Society's
OL,14,Fchairman, said the approval was a
OL,15,Fmilestone in a campaign that began
OL,16,Fback in 2014.
OL,18,F"The reason that this is significant
OL,19,Fis we can start getting machinery into
OL,20,Fthe tunnel and start maintenance for
OL,21,Fit" he explained.
