OL,3,CRhondda Tunnel reopening plans get
OL,4,Cmajor boost as planning application
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,F"It'll be another couple of years
OL,8,Fbefore the tunnel opens completely,
OL,9,Fbut this phase is absolutely crucial".
OL,11,FThe Society has taken ownership of the
OL,12,Fformer Glenrhondda Colliery site close
OL,13,Fto the Blaencwm entrance.
OL,15,FUnder the plans, thousands of tonnes
OL,16,Fof colliery spoil that had been used
OL,17,Fto cover the portal would be moved to
OL,18,Fthe Glenrhondda site, and landscaped
OL,19,Fas the first stage of a country park.
