OL,4,Cmajor boost as planning application
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FRegular access to the tunnel itself
OL,8,Fwill remain off limits for the time
OL,9,Fbeing.
OL,11,FIt remains in the ownership of
OL,12,FHighways England. In 2021, the then UK
OL,13,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps said
OL,14,Fhe would be prepared to hand the
OL,15,Ftunnel over to the Welsh Government or
OL,16,Fanother organisation.
OL,18,FIn June 2025, the Society announced a
OL,19,Fpartnership with charity Railway Paths
OL,20,FLimited, who hope to take on the
OL,21,Fownership of the tunnel.
